    <head><placeName key="PL000000009145">新林寺</placeName><persName key="A014887">道容</persName>尼傳十</head><p><anchor n="T.50.2063.0936b12"/><lb ed="T" n="0936b12"/><persName key="A014887">道容</persName>，本<ptr target="fn24"/><placeName key="PL000000016269">歷陽</placeName>人，住<placeName key="PL000000016237">烏江寺</placeName>。戒行精峻，善占<lb ed="T" n="0936b13"/>吉凶，逆知禍福，世傳為聖。<persName key="A002676">晉明帝</persName>時，甚見敬<lb ed="T" n="0936b14"/>事，以花布席下驗其凡聖，果不萎焉。及<persName key="A002777">簡文<lb ed="T" n="0936b15"/>帝</persName>，先事清水道師，道師<placeName key="PL000000008976">京都</placeName>所謂<persName key="A014889">王濮陽</persName>也。<lb ed="T" n="0936b16"/>第內為立道舍，<persName key="A014887">容</persName>亟開導，未之從也。後<ptr target="fn25"/>宮人<lb ed="T" n="0936b17"/>每入道屋，輒見神人為沙門形，滿於室內。<persName key="A002777">帝</persName><lb ed="T" n="0936b18"/>疑<persName key="A014887">容</persName>所為也，而莫能決。踐祚之後，烏巢太極<lb ed="T" n="0936b19"/>殿。<persName key="A002777">帝</persName>使曲安遠筮之，云：「西南有女人師，能滅<lb ed="T" n="0936b20"/>此怪。」<ref target="#A002777" type="person">帝</ref> 遣使往<placeName key="PL000000016237">烏江</placeName>迎<persName key="A014887">道容</persName>，以事訪之，<ptr target="fn26"/><persName key="A014887">容</persName><lb ed="T" n="0936b21"/>曰：「唯有清齋七日，受持八戒，自當消弭。」<ref target="#A002777" type="person">帝</ref>即<lb ed="T" n="0936b22"/>從之，整肅一心，七日未滿，群烏競集，運巢而<lb ed="T" n="0936b23"/>去。<ref target="#A002777" type="person">帝</ref>深信重，即為立寺，資給所須，因林為名，<lb ed="T" n="0936b24"/>名曰<placeName key="PL000000009145">新林</placeName>，即以師禮事之，遂奉正<ptr target="fn27"/>法。<date key="j18652221874650" notAfter-iso="0420" notBefore-iso="0394">後晉</date><lb ed="T" n="0936b25"/>顯尚佛，<persName key="A014887">道容</persName>之力也。<ptr target="fn28"/>逮<persName key="A002681">孝武</persName>時，彌相崇敬。<date from-iso="0376-02-10" key="j18584311866007" to-iso="0396-11-07">太<lb ed="T" n="0936b26"/>元</date>中，忽而絕跡講不知所在。<ref target="#A002681" type="person">帝</ref>勅<ptr target="fn29"/>葬其衣鉢，<lb ed="T" n="0936b27"/>故<ref target="#PL000000009145" type="place">寺</ref>邊有塚<ptr target="fn＊"/>云。
    </p>
